9 July</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Bloggers%27+imprisonment+sparks+free-speech+rallies&amp;rft.pub=Columbia+Daily+Tribune&amp;rft.date=2013-04-26&amp;rft.aulast=Spory&amp;rft.aufirst=Karyn&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.columbiatribune.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fbloggers-imprisonment-sparks-free-speech-rallies%2Farticle_3d0ed108-ae9d-11e2-b409-10604b9f6eda.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorldwide+Protests+for+Free+Expression+in+Bangladesh\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Blogger_killed-2-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Blogger_killed-2_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://bdnews24.com/bangladesh/2013/02/15/shahbagh-protest-to-go-relentless\">\"Shahbagh protest to go relentless\"</a>. <i>bdnews24.com</i>. 15 February 2013<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 February</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=bdnews24.com&amp;rft.atitle=Shahbagh+protest+to+go+relentless&amp;rft.date=2013-02-15&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbdnews24.com%2Fbangladesh%2F2013%2F02%2F15%2Fshahbagh-protest-to-go-relentless&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorldwide+Protests+for+Free+Expression+in+Bangladesh\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.banglanews24.com/English/detailsnews.php?nssl=1332bd1dc7cf036ce3e30a2e3bd94cc3&amp;nttl=0903201365537\">\"Blogger Saniur files case\"</a>. banglanews24.com. 2013-03-09<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2013-06-18</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Blogger+Saniur+files+case&amp;rft.date=2013-03-09&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.banglanews24.com%2FEnglish%2Fdetailsnews.php%3Fnssl%3D1332bd1dc7cf036ce3e30a2e3bd94cc3%26nttl%3D0903201365537&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorldwide+Protests+for+Free+Expression+in+Bangladesh\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/04/06/hardline-muslims-rally-bangladesh/2058851/\">\"Hardline Muslims rally in Bangladesh amid shutdown\"</a>. Associated Press. 6 April 2013<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">29 July</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Hardline+Muslims+rally+in+Bangladesh+amid+shutdown&amp;rft.pub=Associated+Press&amp;rft.date=2013-04-06&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F2013%2F04%2F06%2Fhardline-muslims-rally-bangladesh%2F2058851%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorldwide+Protests+for+Free+Expression+in+Bangladesh\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-monitoring_panel-1-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-monitoring_panel-1_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/protestors-demand