s\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ifex.org/bangladesh/2013/04/04/bloggers_arrested/\">\"Four Bangladeshi bloggers arrested for \"blasphemous\" posts\"</a>. <i>ifex</i>. 4 April 2013<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">7 April</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=ifex&amp;rft.atitle=Four+Bangladeshi+bloggers+arrested+for+%22blasphemous%22+posts&amp;rft.date=2013-04-04&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifex.org%2Fbangladesh%2F2013%2F04%2F04%2Fbloggers_arrested%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorldwide+Protests+for+Free+Expression+in+Bangladesh\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Asif-1-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Asif-1_10-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.thedailystar.net/beta2/news/blogger-asif-arrested/\">\"Blogger Asif arrested\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Daily_Star_(Bangladesh)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Daily Star (Bangladesh)\">Daily Star (Bangladesh)</a></i>. 4 April 2013<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">7 April</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Daily+Star+%28Bangladesh%29&amp;rft.atitle=Blogger+Asif+arrested&amp;rft.date=2013-04-04&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Fbeta2%2Fnews%2Fblogger-asif-arrested%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorldwide+Protests+for+Free+Expression+in+Bangladesh\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-removeAsif-1-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-removeAsif-1_11-0\">^</a><